Background

The spread of COVID-19 has severely taken affair in over 200 countries worldwide. The outbreak was first detected in mainland China in December 2019. It was reported COVID-19 were originated from wet market in Wuhan, China. The virus could lead to an effect from mild to moderate upper-respiratory tract illnesses for instance Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome (SARS), Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS) and Common Cold. According to World Health Organization (WHO) the transmissions are still under research.

Transmission of corona virus infection can be spread through;

  • Airborne (aerosol), ex: dust or any kind of microbe
  • Droplet spray and direct contact, ex: sneeze, hand shake
  • Indirect (fomite), ex : Towel, doorknob, elevator button

source: https://www.annualreviews.org/doi/pdf/10.1146/annurev-virology-012420-022445

COVID-19 statistic situation by WHO as at 16th June 2020;

  • 7,823,289 confirmed cases
  • 431,541 deaths

source: https://covid19.who.int/

OBJECTIVE

COVID-19 Self Checker serve a purpose to diagnose and inform the user if they are exposed to COVID-19 based on input below

  • Symptom (Cough, Fever, Sore Throat, Shortness of Breath, Headache)
  • Age (either above 60 or below)
  • Gender
  • Travel history
  • Close contact with positive patient

Good News for the Travel Addict!!!

It is also a platform to indentify affected country area of COVID-19 in Worldwide. A music to ears for those globetrotter who like to travel. This could help them to prepare and take a precaution before visiting to the country upon COVID-19 pandemic.
